lead_paragraph: Stephen Strasburg has a strained flexor mass in his elbow and the Washington Nationals don't know when he will pitch again, but the team said it was relieved the right-hander did not re-tear a ligament.

headline.print_headline: Nationals Say Stephen Strasburg Has a Strained Flexor Mass
